              "type": "lab.html.Form",
              "content": "\u003Cmain class=\"content-horizontal-center\"\u003E\n  \n  \u003Cdiv class=\"alert w-l text-left\"\u003E\n    \u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\n  \u003Cp\u003E\n    While reading the following sample, \u003Cstrong\u003Eplease use your keyboard to navigate\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E. ⌨ ➡ 📄📄 \u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\u003Cbr \u002F\u003E For example, when you reach the bottom of a page, tap the right arrow key \u003Ckbd\u003E➡\u003C\u002Fkbd\u003E on your keyboard to advance the page forward.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E \n\u003Cp\u003EReminder: your timing will be recorded, so please \u003Cstrong\u003Eavoid taking breaks\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E during this section and try to maintain a comfortable, normal pace.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n    \u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\n\n\n\u003C\u002Fmain\u003E\n\u003Cfooter\u003E\n  \u003Cform id=\"a_primer\"\u003E\n  \u003Cbutton class=\"black-btn\" type=\"submit\" form=\"a_primer\"\u003EBegin\u003C\u002Fbutton\u003E\n  \u003C\u002Fform\u003E\n\u003C\u002Ffooter\u003E",
