              "type": "lab.html.Form",
              "content": "\u003Cmain class=\"content-horizontal-center\"\u003E\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"alert w-l text-left\"\u003E\n  \u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\u003Cbr \u002F\u003E \u003Cbr \u002F\u003E \u003Cbr \u002F\u003E\n  \u003Cp\u003EThe article will now continue.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n    \u003Cp\u003EWhile reading the following text, please use \u003Cstrong\u003Eyour mouse wheel 🖱 or trackpad\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E (or other pointing device) to navigate by scrolling down the page.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\n    \u003Cp\u003ENote: if this is not possible or is challenging, please navigate the article in any way that you find most comfortable and efficient.\n  \u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n  \u003Cp\u003EReminder: the time it takes you to read will be recorded, so please \u003Cstrong\u003Eavoid taking breaks\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E during this section and try to maintain a comfortable, normal pace.\n  \u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n    \u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\n\n\n\u003C\u002Fmain\u003E\n\u003Cfooter\u003E\n  \u003Cform id=\"a_primer\"\u003E\n  \u003Cbutton class=\"black-btn\" type=\"submit\" form=\"a_primer\"\u003EBegin\u003C\u002Fbutton\u003E\n  \u003C\u002Fform\u003E\n\u003C\u002Ffooter\u003E",
